	securities activities may involve securities and instruments of Rio Tinto or its subsidiaries. The underwriters and their respective affiliates may also make investment recommendations or publish or express independent research views in respect of
	such securities or instruments and may at any time hold, or recommend to clients that they acquire, long or short positions in such securities and instruments.




