Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 8:07 AM ET
Diversified Financial Services

Company Overview of Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited conducts financing activities for the Rio Tinto group of companies. The company is based in Melbourne, Australia. Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited is a subsidiary of Rio Tinto Limited.


120 Collins StreetLevel 33Melbourne, VIC 3000Australia










Key Executives for Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited


Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited does not have any Key Executives recorded. 



Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited Key Developments

Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited Launches New Debt Reduction Program for Up to $2.5 Billion
May 22 17
Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited announced that it will use its strong liquidity position to further reduce gross debt, launching a bond purchase plan for up to $2.5 billion. Under the plan, Rio Tinto has issued a redemption notice for approximately $1.72 billion of its 2019 and 2020 US dollar-denominated notes and commenced cash tender offers to purchase up to approximately $781 million of its five 2021, 2022 and 2025 US dollar-denominated notes. The announcement is part of the Rio Tinto Group's ongoing capital management plan and follows the successful completion of a series of $7.5 billion US dollar-denominated note redemptions and repurchases in 2016. Rio Tinto issued a notice of redemption for all of its 9.000% notes due May 1, 2019 and for all of its 3.500% notes due November 2, 2020 issued by Rio Tinto Finance (USA) Limited. These notes are guaranteed by Rio Tinto plc and Rio Tinto Limited. Approximately $1.719 billion in aggregate principal amount is outstanding. The redemption date is June 21, 2017.


